WEBVTT

00:02:28.305 --> 00:02:30.386
ommabop emas edi.

00:02:30.386 --> 00:02:33.305
O'sha paytlarda kattaroq ansambllar
mashhur bo'lib,

00:02:33.305 --> 00:02:36.925
ular yog'och va mis puflama
va zarbli cholg'ulardan foydalanishgan.

00:02:36.925 --> 00:02:42.358
Ammo Vivaldi uchun bitta skripka,
torlar va klavesin yetarli edi.

00:02:42.358 --> 00:02:44.186
Zamondoshi Baxdan farqli o'laroq,

00:02:44.186 --> 00:02:48.005
Vivaldini murakkab polifonik fugalar
qiziqtirmas edi.

00:02:48.005 --> 00:02:52.036
U bizga buni avvalroq tinglaganimizni
eslatib turuvchi va doimiy takrorlanuvchi,

00:02:52.036 --> 00:02:54.512
tinglovchilar uchun oddiy 
va yengil bo'lgan

00:02:54.512 --> 00:02:58.037
navolarni ko'proq afzal ko'rar edi.

00:02:58.037 --> 00:03:02.026
"Bahor" ning birinchi qismi
bahor kuyi bilan boshlanib,